\mt2 Moęž‰foęž‰s We Foęž‰l Eyoęž‰  
\mt1 Taitus  
\mt2 Emoęž‰ Saęž‰saęž‰ligaęž‰foęž‰  
\imt1 Asulumaęž‰noęž‰ towoęž‰ we  
\ip Moęž‰foęž‰s we Foęž‰l eyoęž‰ Taitusboęž‰woęž‰ saęž‰saęž‰ligaęž‰foęž‰. Tamin amioęž‰ Foęž‰l oęž‰liaęž‰ Taitus oęž‰liaęž‰ haęž‰naęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰, hoęž‰naęž‰loęž‰ hegefaęž‰ hen nowoęž‰ Kilit, aęž‰laęž‰yoęž‰ aęž‰na ane. Aęž‰laęž‰yoęž‰ to nafayoęž‰ widaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰, Foęž‰l e hen nowa haęž‰nakiyoęž‰, Taitus e Kilit saęž‰s hoęž‰giyoęž‰ boęž‰foęž‰meleaęž‰ki, aęž‰na taęž‰foęž‰. Aęž‰laęž‰foęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ Foęž‰l eyoęž‰ Taitusboęž‰woęž‰ asuloęž‰woęž‰ dimiakiyoęž‰, Kilit saęž‰soęž‰ halaidoęž‰ domaęž‰ki moęž‰foęž‰s we aęž‰na saęž‰saęž‰ligaęž‰foęž‰.  
\ip Moęž‰foęž‰s saęž‰saęž‰loęž‰ us wenamioęž‰ to haęž‰g noloęž‰ daęž‰lab. Nowoęž‰ Taitus eyoęž‰ Keliso kalukaęž‰isale ini manoęž‰ dibebeaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰, saęž‰s misaęž‰ kalukaęž‰isaleyoęž‰ daęž‰femaęž‰ki, Foęž‰l eyoęž‰ widoęž‰. Nowoęž‰ Taitus e koęž‰goęž‰doęž‰ kalukaęž‰isale oęž‰liaęž‰ kalukaęž‰isale soęž‰wa oęž‰liaęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ madali nanogdoęž‰ dian kalukaęž‰isale imoęž‰woęž‰ manoęž‰ walamaęž‰ki, Foęž‰l eyoęž‰ widoęž‰. Nowoęž‰ Kilit Keliso kalukaęž‰isaleyoęž‰ manoęž‰ nafale dimidaki, nolboęž‰woęž‰ haęž‰foęž‰ disaęž‰laki towaęž‰yoęž‰ moęž‰kegemaęž‰ki, Foęž‰l eyoęž‰ to we aęž‰na saęž‰saęž‰ligaęž‰foęž‰.  
\c 1  
\p
\v 1 Ne Foęž‰l, Godeyaęž‰ ene nanogdoęž‰ dian kalu nowoęž‰ ne. Yaęž‰su Kelisowaęž‰loęž‰ iligaęž‰feloęž‰ kalu nowoęž‰ ne. Aęž‰laęž‰foęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ Godeyaęž‰loęž‰ daęž‰fe alifeloęž‰ kalukaęž‰isale nolbaęž‰ tilidabu aęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ halale alitakiyoęž‰, Godeyaęž‰ to man hendele aęž‰noęž‰ fanda asulaęž‰ meleaęž‰kiyoęž‰, ne nanog we dimidamaęž‰ki daęž‰feyoęž‰.  
\v 2 \x - \xo 1.2 \xt Kolo 1.27\x*Aęž‰laęž‰goęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ tilidabu aęž‰noęž‰liaęž‰ asuloęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ dialikiyoęž‰, iyoęž‰ melaęž‰noęž‰ melaęž‰noęž‰ sagalaęž‰liki yasilimaęž‰ib. Moęž‰woęž‰ Gode e moęž‰dikili saęž‰lan koęž‰loęž‰, eyoęž‰ taminde amioęž‰ gioęž‰ melaęž‰noęž‰ melaęž‰noęž‰woęž‰ diaęž‰ib aęž‰laęž‰liki saefaęž‰.  
\v 3 Aęž‰laęž‰saefaęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ hoęž‰lendeyoęž‰ faęž‰laęž‰dowabiki, Gode eyoęž‰ ene to aęž‰noęž‰ kalaba faęž‰laęž‰do alifaęž‰. To aęž‰noęž‰ kalaba faęž‰laęž‰domaęž‰kiyoęž‰, Gode niloęž‰ gasili aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ to aęž‰noęž‰ nolboęž‰woęž‰ walamaęž‰kiyoęž‰, nemoęž‰ dimi.   
\p
\v 4 \x - \xo 1.4 \xt Lom 1.7, 2Kol 8.23, Gala 2.3\x*Taitus, naęž‰noęž‰ tilidabuwoęž‰ imilig dowoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰, ge noęž‰noęž‰n soęž‰wale dowabikiyoęž‰, niyoęž‰ moęž‰foęž‰s we gemoęž‰ saęž‰saęž‰ligaęž‰toęž‰l. Haęž‰foęž‰ disaęž‰lan manoęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ haęž‰sa dowan man aęž‰noęž‰ ge oęž‰liaęž‰ meleaęž‰ki, niyoęž‰ Do Gode oęž‰liaęž‰ niloęž‰ aęž‰maęž‰laęž‰ gasili Yaęž‰su Keliso oęž‰liaęž‰moęž‰woęž‰ dulugu soęž‰loęž‰l.   
\s1 Saęž‰s amiloęž‰ misaęž‰ kaluwaęž‰ man dibebeakiloęž‰ daęž‰feanoęž‰ we  
\p
\v 5 Niyoęž‰ ge Kilit hoęž‰naęž‰loęž‰ hegefaęž‰ hen aęž‰namiloęž‰ taęž‰foęž‰woęž‰ moęž‰woęž‰ we. Nanogoęž‰ moęž‰kedefoęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ gi dimidaki aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ Kilit amisaęž‰noęž‰ tambo amioęž‰ niloęž‰ gemoęž‰loęž‰ sioęž‰ aumboęž‰, saęž‰sdoęž‰ boęž‰foęž‰lowan kaluwoęž‰ daęž‰femaęž‰ki, aęž‰na taęž‰foęž‰.  
\v 6 \x - \xo 1.6 \xt 1Tim 3.2-7, 2Tim 2.24-26\x*Giyoęž‰ saęž‰s amiloęž‰ misaęž‰ kaluwoęž‰ daęž‰femaęž‰nikiyoęž‰, kalu we oęž‰ngoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ daęž‰feaęž‰bi. Eyoęž‰ man digaloęž‰le kudu haęž‰naki, kalu nolbaęž‰yoęž‰ e hala dimidab aęž‰laęž‰boęž‰ moęž‰asulaęž‰sen. E gayoęž‰ imilig di. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ kalu ene soęž‰wagalin aęž‰noęž‰ Kelisowa tilidaęž‰daęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰, kalukaęž‰isaleyaęž‰ siwaęž‰l amioęž‰ iyoęž‰ moęž‰aęž‰laęž‰iyaki, iya oęž‰liaęž‰ ano oęž‰liaęž‰maęž‰ towoęž‰ kudu haęž‰naęž‰sen aęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ daęž‰feaęž‰bi.  
\v 7 Saęž‰sdoęž‰ boęž‰foęž‰lowan kalu iyoęž‰, Godeyaęž‰ ene nanog boęž‰foęž‰lowaęž‰sen koęž‰loęž‰ giliyoęž‰ kalu we oęž‰ngoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ daęž‰feaęž‰bi. Eyoęž‰ man digaloęž‰le kudu haęž‰naki, kalu nolbaęž‰yoęž‰ e hala dimidab aęž‰laęž‰boęž‰ moęž‰asulaęž‰sen. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ e kalu alan aęž‰lakiyoęž‰, kalukaęž‰isaleyoęž‰ moęž‰waęž‰laęž‰saęž‰ndan. E boęž‰eboęž‰ moęž‰gadian. E alunaęž‰ hoęž‰noęž‰ noęž‰nolomaęž‰noęž‰woęž‰ moęž‰nan. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ nol oęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ moęž‰buban. E mole alan diaęž‰noęž‰woęž‰ moęž‰meselan.   
\p
\v 8 Man oęž‰leoęž‰ngoęž‰woęž‰ moęž‰dimidaki, e magesoęž‰ kaluwoęž‰ dinafa tilidowan. E man nafale dimidamaęž‰noęž‰ asulan. E asuloęž‰woęž‰ nafale kudu haęž‰nan. Ene man digaloęž‰le, Godeyaęž‰loęž‰ asulab aęž‰noęž‰loęž‰ kudu haęž‰naęž‰sen. Ene asuloęž‰woęž‰ dinafa tilidowan.  
\v 9 To hendele emoęž‰loęž‰ widoęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰, eyoęž‰ dinafa halale taęž‰li silikiyoęž‰, kalukaęž‰isale nolbaęž‰ tilidabuwoęž‰ halaidoęž‰ domaęž‰ki man aęž‰noęž‰ widaęž‰sen. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ Godeyaęž‰ toloęž‰ gola baęž‰daęž‰sen kalukaęž‰isale i aęž‰noęž‰ to we hendeleloęž‰b aęž‰laęž‰boęž‰ fanda asulumaęž‰ki, man aęž‰noęž‰ eyoęž‰ widaęž‰sen. \fig Saęž‰sdoęž‰ boęž‰foęž‰lowan kalu iliyoęž‰ magesoęž‰ kaluwoęž‰ dinafa tilidowan.|alt="Guests in home" src="BA03023BW.tif" size="col" copy="Used with permission of Louise Bass." ref="1.8" \fig*   
\p
\v 10 \x - \xo 1.10 \xt 1Tim 4.7\x*Moęž‰woęž‰ Kilit saęž‰s us aęž‰namioęž‰, toloęž‰ sanditan man oęž‰liaęž‰, madali toloęž‰ saęž‰lan man oęž‰liaęž‰, dikili saęž‰lan man aęž‰noęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ kalukaęž‰isaleyoęž‰ modoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ kudu haęž‰naęž‰lab. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ kalu nolbaęž‰yoęž‰ Yuma Keliso kalukaęž‰isale aęž‰noęž‰ Yuwaęž‰ eleyoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ oęž‰kudu hamanaęž‰kiloęž‰ dibodaęž‰sen iliyoęž‰loęž‰ man aęž‰noęž‰ alan dimidaęž‰lab.  
\v 11 \x - \xo 1.11 \xt 2Tim 3.5-6, 1Bid 5.2\x*Iliyoęž‰ mole afale diaęž‰noęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰liki, nililoęž‰ moęž‰dimidan man aęž‰noęž‰ widaęž‰lab koęž‰loęž‰, kalukaęž‰isale nol oęž‰liaęž‰ ini soęž‰loęž‰ oęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ asuloęž‰woęž‰ noęž‰nolo alitakiyoęž‰, ili tilidabuwoęž‰ ka taęž‰tab. Aęž‰laęž‰foęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ iliyoęž‰ to man aęž‰noęž‰ waęž‰kabiyoęž‰ widabenaęž‰ki kaęž‰laęž‰bi.   
\p
\v 12 Tamin amioęž‰ asuloęž‰loęž‰ di kalu nowoęž‰ Kilit hen aęž‰na ilikiyoęž‰, towoęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰saęž‰saęž‰loęž‰, â€śKilit kalukaęž‰isaleyoęž‰ madali towoęž‰ saęž‰laęž‰sen. Iyoęž‰ saila gasayoęž‰ oęž‰ngoęž‰ dowaęž‰sen. Iyoęž‰ boęž‰sulakiyoęž‰, maęž‰noęž‰woęž‰ besagali naęž‰sen.â€ť  
\v 13-14 \x - \xo 1.13-14 \xt 1Tim 4.7, 2Tim 4.2\x*To we mada hendele saęž‰saęž‰loęž‰. Aęž‰laęž‰foęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ kalukaęž‰isale ili tilidabu aęž‰noęž‰ halaidoęž‰ domaęž‰ki, aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ iliyoęž‰ Yuwaęž‰ kandayoęž‰ malolab aęž‰namidaęž‰yoęž‰ moęž‰iligi dabumaęž‰ki, aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ to hendeleloęž‰ moęž‰kudu haęž‰nab kaluwaęž‰loęž‰ ele difaęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰, moęž‰kudu hamanaęž‰kiyoęž‰, giyoęž‰ halale saęž‰laki, i aęž‰noęž‰ digalaki widaęž‰bi.  
\v 15 Kalukaęž‰isale abeyoęž‰ Godeyaęž‰ siwaęž‰l amioęž‰ asugoęž‰ goęž‰goęž‰doęž‰loęž‰ aęž‰lab i aęž‰namioęž‰, kelegoęž‰woęž‰ tambo nafale dowoęž‰. Koęž‰sega kalukaęž‰isale abeyoęž‰ Yaęž‰suwoęž‰ moęž‰tilidaęž‰dakiloęž‰, asuloęž‰woęž‰ mogagoęž‰ aęž‰lab i amioęž‰, kelegoęž‰woęž‰ tambo mogagoęž‰le dowab. Kalu i aęž‰noęž‰ ili asuloęž‰waęž‰loęž‰ nafale alobaęž‰dan aęž‰noęž‰ mogagilaęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰lab.  
\v 16 \x - \xo 1.16 \xt 1Yoęž‰n 1.6, 2.4\x*Iliyoęž‰ â€śNe Godeyoęž‰ mada asuloęž‰â€ť aęž‰laęž‰saęž‰laęž‰lab koęž‰sega, ililoęž‰ man dimidab aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰, iyoęž‰ Godeyoęž‰ moęž‰baęž‰dan aęž‰laęž‰ widakigab. Aęž‰laęž‰foęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ Gode eyoęž‰ kalu oęž‰moęž‰woęž‰ mada mogagoęž‰le baęž‰daęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰ moęž‰beab. Iyoęž‰ Godeyaęž‰loęž‰ sioęž‰ aumboęž‰ moęž‰kudu haęž‰nakiyoęž‰, i aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ man nafa dimidamaęž‰noęž‰woęž‰ moęž‰ililoęž‰.   
\c 2  
\s1 Koęž‰goęž‰doęž‰ kalukaęž‰isalemoęž‰loęž‰ to widoęž‰woęž‰ we  
\p
\v 1 Taitus giyoęž‰ to man widakiyoęž‰, to hendele oęž‰liaęž‰loęž‰ ililoęž‰ dowab aęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ widaęž‰bi.  
\v 2 Kalu koęž‰goęž‰doęž‰le sab oęž‰moęž‰woęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰widaęž‰bi. â€śKalu koęž‰goęž‰doęž‰ gioęž‰ moęž‰noęž‰nolo dowaki, asuloęž‰ nafaleyoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ kudu haęž‰naęž‰lubi. Giliyoęž‰ manoęž‰ nafale dimidaki, goęž‰noęž‰n aęž‰maęž‰laęž‰yoęž‰ tili dowaęž‰lubi. Tilidabu manoęž‰, haęž‰foęž‰ disaęž‰lan manoęž‰, aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ hidaęž‰yoęž‰ faęž‰laęž‰dowalikiloęž‰ halale kagamaęž‰noęž‰ man aęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ kudu haęž‰naęž‰lubi.â€ť Giyoęž‰ imoęž‰woęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰widaęž‰bi.  
\v 3 \x - \xo 2.3 \xt 1Tim 3.11\x*Taitus giyoęž‰, kaęž‰isale koęž‰goęž‰doęž‰ sab imoęž‰woęž‰ towoęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰widaęž‰bi. â€śKaęž‰isale koęž‰goęž‰doęž‰ giliyoęž‰ Godeyaęž‰loęž‰ asulab au dimidakiyoęž‰, noloęž‰ sadaęž‰daęž‰soęž‰bo. Alunaęž‰ hoęž‰n nab aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ gili asuloęž‰woęž‰ moęž‰tilidomaęž‰ki taęž‰taęž‰bi. Man digaloęž‰ mesaęž‰noęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ widaęž‰li haęž‰naęž‰bi.â€ť  
\v 4-5 \x - \xo 2.4-5 \xt Aęž‰fe 5.22\x*Giyoęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰widalikiyoęž‰, kaęž‰isale koęž‰goęž‰doęž‰ iliyoęž‰loęž‰ kaęž‰isale kalu hoęž‰giloęž‰ ane imoęž‰woęž‰loęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰widaęž‰bi. Kalu giloęž‰ oęž‰liaęž‰ soęž‰wa giloęž‰ oęž‰liaęž‰moęž‰woęž‰ haęž‰foęž‰woęž‰ disaęž‰laęž‰lubi. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ gioęž‰ asuloęž‰ nafale kudu haęž‰naki, maliloęž‰ man aęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ kudu haęž‰naęž‰lubi. Gioęž‰ kalu goęž‰ndoęž‰maęž‰ haęž‰ga dowaki, ginin soęž‰loęž‰woęž‰ dinafa boęž‰foęž‰lubi. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ gioęž‰ nowoęž‰mboęž‰woęž‰loęž‰ sagale alitaęž‰bi. Kalukaęž‰isale nolbaęž‰yoęž‰ Godeyaęž‰ to nafa aęž‰noęž‰ dioęž‰ge saęž‰labenaęž‰kiyoęž‰, kaęž‰isale i aęž‰noęž‰ man we koęž‰loęž‰ kudu hamanaęž‰ki widaęž‰bi.   
\s1 Kalu soęž‰wamoęž‰loęž‰ to widoęž‰woęž‰ we  
\p
\v 6 Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ kalu soęž‰wa iliyoęž‰ asuloęž‰ nafaleyoęž‰ kudu hamanaęž‰ki, iyoęž‰ halale alitaęž‰bi.  
\v 7 \x - \xo 2.7 \xt 1Tim 4.12\x*Iliyoęž‰ man giloęž‰woęž‰ baęž‰daęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰ kudu menaęž‰ki, giyoęž‰ kelegoęž‰ tambo dimidakiyoęž‰, manoęž‰ nafale dimidaęž‰bi. Giyoęž‰ manoęž‰ widakiyoęž‰, man digaloęž‰le kudu haęž‰naki, aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ to giloęž‰ saęž‰lab aęž‰noęž‰ hendele aęž‰laęž‰asulumaęž‰ki widaęž‰bi.  
\v 8 \x - \xo 2.8 \xt 1Bid 2.15\x*Giyoęž‰ to man widakiyoęž‰, to nafale digaloęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰koęž‰ saęž‰laęž‰lubi. Aęž‰laęž‰dimidalikiyoęž‰, nililoęž‰ mogagoęž‰ dimidoęž‰ imilig nowoęž‰ gis kaluwaęž‰yoęž‰ moęž‰baęž‰baęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰, to saęž‰maęž‰noęž‰woęž‰ aundoęž‰ma dowaki, iyoęž‰ sendelomaęž‰ib.   
\s1 Madali nanogdoęž‰ dian kalukaęž‰isalemoęž‰loęž‰ to widoęž‰woęž‰ we  
\p
\v 9-10 \x - \xo 2.9-10 \xt 1Tim 6.1\x*Giyoęž‰ madali nanogdoęž‰ dian kalukaęž‰isalemoęž‰woęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰widaęž‰bi. â€śNanog dian kalukaęž‰isale gioęž‰, kelegoęž‰ tambo amioęž‰ giloęž‰ boęž‰foęž‰lowan kaluwaęž‰ haęž‰ga iliki, towoęž‰ aęž‰maęž‰laęž‰boęž‰ saęž‰laęž‰soęž‰bo. Boęž‰foęž‰lowan kaluwoęž‰ sagale alitaęž‰bi. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ boęž‰foęž‰lowan kaluwaęž‰ kelegoęž‰woęž‰ afaleboęž‰ diaęž‰soęž‰bo. Koęž‰sega giloęž‰ boęž‰foęž‰lowan kaluwaęž‰yoęž‰ gioęž‰ tili asulumaęž‰kiyoęž‰, giliyoęž‰ hoęž‰lenoęž‰ tambo man digaloęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ kudu haęž‰naęž‰lubi.â€ť Iliyoęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰dimidalikiyoęž‰, kalukaęž‰isale nolbaęž‰yoęž‰ ililoęž‰ dimidab aęž‰noęž‰ baęž‰daęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰, Godeyaęž‰loęž‰ ni koęž‰loęž‰ gasili to widaęž‰lab aęž‰noęž‰ hendeleloęž‰b aęž‰laęž‰boęž‰ asulakiyoęž‰, to aęž‰noęž‰ iyoęž‰loęž‰ kudu haęž‰naęž‰noęž‰ asulumaęž‰ib.   
\s1 Yaęž‰su miaęž‰noęž‰ yasilakiyoęž‰, man nafale dimidaęž‰bi.  
\p
\v 11 Godeyaęž‰loęž‰ haęž‰foęž‰ disaęž‰lan man aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ kalukaęž‰isaleyoęž‰ oęž‰lika gasiliaęž‰ib koęž‰loęž‰, man aęž‰noęž‰ kalukaęž‰isale tamboloęž‰ amioęž‰ kalaba faęž‰laęž‰dowoęž‰.  
\v 12 \x - \xo 2.12 \xt 1Yoęž‰n 2.16\x*Godeyaęž‰loęž‰ moęž‰asulab aęž‰noęž‰liaęž‰ doęž‰moęž‰waęž‰loęž‰ asulan man aęž‰noęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ kataęž‰fomaęž‰kiyoęž‰, Godeyaęž‰ ene haęž‰foęž‰ disaęž‰lan man aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ nimoęž‰woęž‰ widaęž‰lab. Man aęž‰noęž‰ taęž‰takiyoęž‰, nioęž‰ henfeloęž‰ wena silikiyoęž‰, asuloęž‰ nafaleloęž‰ kudu haęž‰naęž‰sen man oęž‰liaęž‰, digaloęž‰ domaęž‰noęž‰ man oęž‰liaęž‰, Godeyaęž‰loęž‰ asulab au domaęž‰noęž‰ man oęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ kudu hamanaęž‰ki, widab.  
\v 13 Niloęž‰ gasiliaęž‰noęž‰ Gode Alan oęž‰liaęž‰ Yaęž‰su Keliso eloęž‰ aęž‰maęž‰laęž‰doęž‰ miaęž‰nigab hoęž‰len alan aęž‰noęž‰, nioęž‰ sagalaęž‰li yasilaęž‰likiyoęž‰, man aęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ dimidaęž‰melaęž‰niki.  
\v 14 \x - \xo 2.14 \xt Kis 19.5, Lo 7.6, Ese 37.23, Gala 1.4, 1Bid 2.9\x*Nioęž‰ man mogagoęž‰ dimidaęž‰len amioęž‰ aęž‰maęž‰laęž‰ gasiliaki, aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ nili asuloęž‰woęž‰ maliloęž‰ domaęž‰kiyoęž‰, Yaęž‰su Keliso eyoęž‰ ene melaęž‰noęž‰woęž‰ aęž‰na walaęž‰. Aęž‰laęž‰goęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ kalukaęž‰isale nioęž‰ enoęž‰le domaęž‰ki, aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ manoęž‰ nafale dimidamaęž‰noęž‰ mada asulumaęž‰kiyoęž‰, Yaęž‰suwaęž‰yoęž‰ aęž‰na dimidoęž‰.   
\p
\v 15 \x - \xo 2.15 \xt 1Tim 4.12\x*Aęž‰laęž‰foęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ giyoęž‰ to aęž‰noęž‰ widaęž‰lubi. Giyoęž‰ towoęž‰ halaidoęž‰ widakiyoęž‰, kalukaęž‰isaleyaęž‰ tilidabu aęž‰noęž‰ halale alitakiyoęž‰, mogagoęž‰ dimidoęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ digalaęž‰lubi. Kalukaęž‰isale nolbaęž‰yoęž‰ ge waęž‰laęž‰ saęž‰ndabenaęž‰ki, ge halaidoęž‰ dowaęž‰bi.   
\c 3  
\s1 Man nafale dimidaęž‰bi  
\p
\v 1 \x - \xo 3.1 \xt Lom 13.1-7, 1Bid 2.13-14\x*Taitus giyoęž‰ Kilit Keliso kalukaęž‰isalemoęž‰ aęž‰widakiyoęž‰, iliyoęž‰ gamani misaęž‰ kalu oęž‰liaęž‰ amisaęž‰naęž‰ misaęž‰ kalu oęž‰liaęž‰maęž‰ haęž‰ga dowaki, ililoęž‰ to saęž‰lab aęž‰noęž‰ kudu hamanaęž‰ki widaęž‰bi. Kalukaęž‰isaleyoęž‰ hoęž‰lenoęž‰ tambo man nafa dimidaki kudu hamanaęž‰ki widaęž‰bi.  
\v 2 Kalukaęž‰isale iliyoęž‰ noloęž‰ moęž‰sadaęž‰daki, haęž‰sa domaęž‰ki widaęž‰bi. Wi enedoęž‰woęž‰ moęž‰wabudaki, kalukaęž‰isale tambomoęž‰woęž‰ ege domaęž‰ki widaęž‰bi.   
\p
\v 3 \x - \xo 3.3 \xt 1Kol 6.9-11, Aęž‰fe 2.1-2, 5.8\x*Nioęž‰loęž‰ tamin amioęž‰ babale dowaki aęž‰laęž‰iyakiyoęž‰ moęž‰kudu haęž‰naęž‰sen. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ man koęž‰li koęž‰liloęž‰, nili doęž‰moęž‰waęž‰loęž‰ asulan oęž‰liaęž‰ nili sagalakiloęž‰ dimidaęž‰sen aęž‰noęž‰liaęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰, nioęž‰ dikidabikiyoęž‰, meyaęž‰loęž‰ meloęž‰ oęž‰ngoęž‰ aęž‰maęž‰ susululiaęž‰gaęž‰ haęž‰naęž‰len. Nioęž‰ hoęž‰lenoęž‰ tambo man mogagoęž‰ dimidaęž‰likiyoęž‰, nol oęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ eteaęž‰liki moęž‰beaęž‰sen. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ kalukaęž‰isale nolbaęž‰yoęž‰ nimoęž‰woęž‰ kulufaęž‰yab amioęž‰, niliyoęž‰loęž‰ imoęž‰woęž‰ kulufaęž‰yaęž‰sen.  
\v 4-5 \x - \xo 3.4-5 \xt 2Tim 1.9, Hibu 10.22\x*Koęž‰sega niloęž‰ gasili Gode eyoęž‰ nimoęž‰woęž‰ haęž‰foęž‰ disaęž‰laki, sagale alitaęž‰sen koęž‰loęž‰ nioęž‰ aęž‰maęž‰laęž‰ gasili. Nioęž‰ man digaloęž‰le dimidaęž‰lena gasilima. Koęž‰sega Gode eyoęž‰ nioęž‰ nofolo alitaki, gasili koęž‰loęž‰, ene Mama aęž‰maęž‰ halaidoęž‰waęž‰ ilikiyoęž‰, nioęž‰ toęž‰goęž‰de alifaęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰, nioęž‰ hoęž‰gi aęž‰saęž‰laęž‰liaki, melaęž‰noęž‰ hoęž‰giyoęž‰ dimi.  
\v 6 \x - \xo 3.6 \xt Ilig 2.17-18\x*Niloęž‰ gasili, Yaęž‰su Keliso eya ilikiyoęž‰, Gode eyoęž‰ Ene Mama Maliloęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ boba dimiaki, niya koęž‰goęž‰lu alifeloęž‰.  
\v 7 Eloęž‰ dimidoęž‰woęž‰ moęž‰woęž‰ we. Godeyaęž‰ ene kanuloęž‰ aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ nioęž‰ ene siwaęž‰l amioęž‰ digaloęž‰le taęž‰foęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰, aęž‰na ilikiyoęž‰, nioęž‰ ene soęž‰wale taęž‰taki, melaęž‰noęž‰ melaęž‰noęž‰woęž‰ mada diaęž‰noęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰asulaki yasisoęž‰l.  
\v 8 To aęž‰noęž‰ hendele soęž‰loęž‰l. Kalukaęž‰isale Gode amiloęž‰ tilidabu i aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ man nafa halale dimidamaęž‰noęž‰woęž‰, tamindeyoęž‰ weloęž‰b aęž‰laęž‰asulumaęž‰ki, giyoęž‰ to aęž‰noęž‰ halale widaęž‰bi. Niloęž‰ to widoęž‰l we nafale koęž‰loęž‰, to wemaęž‰yoęž‰ tambo asuwaęž‰faęž‰ib.  
\v 9 \x - \xo 3.9 \xt 2Tim 2.14,16\x*Koęž‰sega giyoęž‰ moęž‰loęž‰ma kabiloęž‰ towaęž‰loęž‰ kegab aęž‰noęž‰liaęž‰, ge maęž‰mu i mioęž‰ agelaęž‰sen aęž‰noęž‰liaęž‰, Moęž‰saęž‰saęž‰ ele saefaęž‰ amiloęž‰ to kegab aęž‰noęž‰liaęž‰, towaęž‰loęž‰ kegab aęž‰noęž‰ tambo taęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰, aęž‰le dowaęž‰bi. Moęž‰woęž‰ towaęž‰loęž‰ kegab aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ fo nafayoęž‰ moęž‰helemaęž‰ib.  
\v 10 \x - \xo 3.10 \xt Madi 18.15-17\x*Saęž‰s us amioęž‰, kalukaęž‰isale imilig nomaęž‰yoęž‰ towaęž‰ kegakiyoęž‰ alobaęž‰maęž‰noęž‰ to saęž‰lalega, giyoęž‰ hagugoęž‰woęž‰ saęž‰laęž‰bi. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ emoęž‰woęž‰ hagugoęž‰ towoęž‰ waęž‰ka sioęž‰ amioęž‰ moęž‰daęž‰dalega, gioęž‰ kalu aęž‰noęž‰ faęž‰s dimiaęž‰bi.  
\v 11 Kalu oęž‰ngoęž‰woęž‰ e asuloęž‰ nafaleyoęž‰ taęž‰taki, man mogagoęž‰le dimidaęž‰lab koęž‰loęž‰, ene mogagoęž‰ dimidoęž‰ aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ e moęž‰walilaęž‰laęž‰gaęž‰ taęž‰li koęž‰loęž‰lab, aęž‰laęž‰boęž‰ ge asuloęž‰.   
\p
\v 12 \x - \xo 3.12 \xt Aęž‰fe 6.21-22, Kolo 4.7-8\x*Niyoęž‰ kalu imilig nowoęž‰, Atemas eyaęž‰le, Tikikus eyaęž‰le geloęž‰wa iligaęž‰faęž‰noęž‰. Taęž‰n hoęž‰len amioęž‰ ne Nikobolis amisaęž‰n aęž‰na mesaęž‰noęž‰ asuloęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰, kalu aęž‰noęž‰ geloęž‰wa faęž‰laęž‰dowaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰yoęž‰, ge ne aęž‰na galimaęž‰ni boęž‰boęž‰ge yaęž‰bi.  
\v 13 \x - \xo 3.13 \xt Ilig 18.24, 1Kol 3.5-6\x*Abolos oęž‰liaęž‰ gamani eleloęž‰ asuloęž‰ kalu, Senas oęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ haęž‰naęž‰nigalikiyoęž‰, aęž‰laęž‰yoęž‰ kelegoęž‰loęž‰ma dowabenaęž‰ki, giyoęž‰ mada asuwaęž‰taęž‰bi.  
\v 14 \x - \xo 3.14 \xt Aęž‰fe 4.28\x*Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ Kilit Keliso kalukaęž‰isaleyaęž‰yoęž‰ kelegoęž‰loęž‰ma kalukaęž‰isaleyoęž‰ halale asuwaęž‰taęž‰ meleaęž‰ki asuloęž‰l. Iliyoęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰dimidalikiyoęž‰, fowoęž‰ nafa hedaki, hoęž‰lenoęž‰ tambo amioęž‰ kelegoęž‰woęž‰ oęž‰li domaęž‰ib.   
\p
\v 15 Kalukaęž‰isale tambo ne oęž‰liaęž‰loęž‰ sab wemaęž‰yoęž‰ gimoęž‰woęž‰ sagaloęž‰ towoęž‰ iligaęž‰tab. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ tilidabu kalukaęž‰isale, ne mili koęž‰loęž‰ gi oęž‰liaęž‰loęž‰ sab nol oęž‰moęž‰woęž‰loęž‰ sagaloęž‰ towoęž‰ saęž‰laęž‰biyoęž‰.  
\p Godeyaęž‰ haęž‰foęž‰ disalanoęž‰ gi oęž‰liaęž‰ dowaęž‰biyoęž‰.   